videos.headline: Moutaineers' Sinkfield runs in for 9-yard TD
videos.description: West Virginia RB Alec Sinkfield breaks out for a 9-yard rushing TD.

videos.headline: Mountaineers' Jennings Jr. punches in TD
videos.description: West Virginia WR Gary Jennings catches an 11-yard touchdown pass from QB Will Grier.

videos.headline: Penguins Joiner dives for a TD catch
videos.description: Youngstown State QB  rips a 4-yard touchdown pass to Miles Joiner to cut into the deficit.

videos.headline: Jennings adds another TD on the night
videos.description: Will Grier finds Gary Jennings Jr. for a 24-yard touchdown to extend the Mountaineers' lead before half.

videos.headline: Jennings completes his 3rd TD of the night
videos.description: West Virginia WR Gary Jennings Jr. scores a 33-yard touchdown, his third of the night.

videos.headline: Penguins' McCaster bursts free for a 13-yard TD
videos.description: Youngstown State RB Tevin McCaster runs in for a 13-yard TD that shrinks West Virginia's lead.

videos.headline: Mountaineers RB Brown scores 1st career rushing TD
videos.description: West Virginia RB Leddie Brown punches it into the end zone from a yard out for his first career rushing touchdown.

videos.headline: McKoy drives in an 8-yard TD
videos.description: West Virginia's Kennedy McKoy brings in an eight-yard rushing touchdown to add to the Mountaineers' route.

videos.headline: Maiden speeds down field for 1st career TD
videos.description: West Virginia WR Dominique Maiden catches a Will Grier pass for a 40-yard touchdown.
